--- 
title: 'Adding a profile picture'
type: 'Tutorial'
--- 

In this tutorial, you will learn how to add a profile picture to your account in Yaas.

1.	Sign into Yaas.
2.	Click My Account on the top of the page. This will open your profile in Yaas.
3.	Click UPLOAD PHOTO. A new window will open.
4.	You may now choose the photo from your computer. Click on the file and then click open. 
5.	You may see the picture you chose on the left.
6.	To save the changes click SAVE in the upper right corner.
7.	Your profile is updated.
